Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:57.37,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}想要向你歌唱  讓你傾聽的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:04.47,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我為了不讓其毀壞而太過於珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:10.39,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也輸入郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:16.26,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又將其刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.66,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.83,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將其打破的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:25.67,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}為我帶來契機的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:29.65,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心將其緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:33.23,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將現在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:36.72,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}雖然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:40.59,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使將碎片全部收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:43.79,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必須用自己的雙手將其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.49,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}極其珍視的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.84,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕將其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:55.53,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.81,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}都存在於此
